item.title: JONONE
item.description: Biographie John Andrew Perello, AKA JonOne is a graffiti artist, borns in 1963 in New York USA. He founded the 156 All Starz group in 1984 in New York. At the age of 17, he began working in the world of graffiti with his childhood friend White Man.
